[b][color=#bf9000][size=3]     [u]How to install[/u]:[/size][/color][/b]
Use NMM or extract to your data folder.
Go into showracemenu, 
Set race to Nord and go to the presets tab, hit F9 to load a preset.
Select the one called "Arabella.jslot" and hit enter.
Enjoy!
